shortForecast: Light Snow Likely then Partly Sunny
name: New Year's Day
detailedForecast: Snow likely before 9am. Partly sunny. High near 31, with temperatures falling to around 19 in the afternoon. West wind 7 to 14 mph, with gusts as high as 29 mph. Chance of precipitation is 70%. New snow accumulation of less than one inch possible.
